text: Arthur Sundbye (September 29, 1879 - December 9, 1949) was an American gymnast. He competed in three events at the 1904 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1879 births Category:1949 deaths Category:American male artistic gymnasts Category:Olympic gymnasts of the United States Category:Gymnasts at the 1904 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Oslo
